        "subject": "LU-5458 lnet: peer aliveness status and NI status",
        "message": "LU-5458 lnet: peer aliveness status and NI status\n\nA couple of changes in this patch:\n- When LNet received a message, it can determine peer of this message\n  is alive\n\n- When LNet recieved a message from remote network, it can determine\n  router is alive and NI status on router is UP.\n\nSigned-off-by: Liang Zhen <liang.zhen@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ib3951ae542de6d50a83b722b33b6e912b6c2e3d4\n"
